giant News Corp failing to offset mixed performances among other
bluechips.
</P>
<P>
The benchmark all ordinaries index finished 9.5 points lower at
3054.4, off a high of 3067.9 during the day.
</P>
<P>
The all industrials index dropped 24.3 points to 5286.7 and the
all resources index finished 5.3 points higher at 1305.3 after
mixed performances among resource stocks.
</P>
