<HEADLINE> ROK's Daewoo Group Invests 3.3 Billion US Dollars in China </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, July 14 (Xinhua) -- The Daewoo Group of the Republic
of Korea (ROK) has established 56 jointly or solely invested
