<HEADLINE> Australia's Star Lifter Might Miss Sydney Olympics </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CANBERRA, July 14 (Xinhua) -- Atlanta Olympic superheavyweight
bronze medallist Stefan Botev may miss next year's Sydney Olympics
after sustaining a serious injury to his shoulder, reports said on
Wednesday.
</P>
